# Alogyan — Modules & Features Brainstorm

## Understanding Lock ✅

| Key | Value |
|-----|-------|
| **What** | Teacher CMS + Public Discovery Platform for tutors & small institutes |
| **Why** | Help non-technical teachers manage students, fees, attendance, tests & notes in one place, and get discovered by new students |
| **Who** | Primary: Individual teachers / small coaching institutes. Secondary: Students + Parents (public pages only) |
| **Constraints** | No built-in payment gateway (teachers use their own UPI/cash). Tests module needs both online Q&A creation AND offline PDF+score entry |
| **Student–Batch model** | Students exist globally under a teacher account, assigned to batches per term (many-to-many) |
| **Non-Goals** | Native mobile app (MVP), multi-teacher org accounts (later), built-in payment processing |

---

## Decision Log

| # | Decision | Alternatives | Reason |
|---|----------|-------------|--------|
| 1 | Students are global, assigned to batches per term | Student per batch only | Flexible re-enrollment, avoids data duplication |
| 2 | No built-in payment gateway | Razorpay/Stripe integration | Teachers already use their own UPI; reduces compliance scope for MVP |
| 3 | Tests = online creation + PDF upload + manual score entry | Online only | Matches hybrid Indian classroom reality |

---

## Full Module Map

### 1. 🏠 Dashboard
**Purpose:** Landing screen. Instant glance at what needs attention today.

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Today's Attendance Summary | % present across all batches |
| Fee Alerts | Count of students with overdue fees |
| Upcoming Classes | Next 3 scheduled timeslots |
| New Leads | Unread enquiries from public profile |
| Recent Activity Feed | Last 5 actions (marked paid, added student, etc.) |
| Quick Action Buttons | + Add Student, + New Batch, + Mark Attendance, + Record Fee |
| Zero State | Onboarding checklist for new teachers (Create Batch → Add Students → first attendance) |

---

### 2. 👤 Students
**Purpose:** Global student roster for the teacher account.

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Student List | Name, Phone, Parent Phone, Grade, Active Batches, Fee Status badge |
| Add Student | Modal: Name, Phone, Parent Phone, Grade, Address (optional) |
| Student Profile | Individual page: bio, batch history, attendance %, fee history, test scores, notes |
| Bulk Import | CSV upload with column mapping |
| Archive / Deactivate | Soft-delete; archived students don't appear in active lists |
| Search & Filter | By name, batch, fee status, grade |
| Export | Download student list as CSV/PDF |

---

### 3. 📚 Batches
**Purpose:** Organize students into class groups (the core CMS unit).

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Batch List | Name, Subject, Schedule, Student Count, Status (Active/Paused/Closed) |
| Create Batch | Name, Subject, Days+Time, Fees per month, Max Seats, Description |
| Batch Detail | Student roster for that batch, attendance history, fee collection status |
| Assign Students | Add/remove students from batch (multi-select picker) |
| Batch Schedule | Recurring schedule (e.g., Mon/Wed/Fri 5–7 PM) |
| Pause / Archive Batch | Stops appearing in active UI without losing historical data |
| Clone Batch | Duplicate batch settings for next term |

---

### 4. ✅ Attendance
**Purpose:** Mark and track daily attendance per batch.

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Quick Mark Screen | Tap Present/Absent for each student in a batch (large touch targets) |
| Bulk Mark All Present | One-tap, then individual corrections |
| Date Picker | Mark attendance retroactively (if teacher forgot) |
| Attendance History | Calendar view per batch — green/red per day |
| Per-Student Report | % attendance this month/term, total classes |
| Absent Alerts | Optional: auto-SMS to parent when student is absent (if phone integrated) |
| Holiday Marking | Mark a date as holiday — excluded from attendance calculation |

---

### 5. 💰 Fees
**Purpose:** Track who has paid and who owes — no built-in payment processing.

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Fee Overview | Per-batch or all-students view: Paid / Pending / Overdue counts |
| Generate Fee Request | Set amount + due date for a batch (creates pending records for all students) |
| Mark Paid | Select mode: Cash / UPI / Cheque / Other. Date + optional memo |
| Partial Payment | Record partial amount paid, show remaining balance |
| Fee History | Per student: full transaction log |
| Custom Fee Amount | Override per-student if different from batch default |
| Dues Report | Export list of students with outstanding fees |
| Optional: Share Payment Info | Teacher can paste their own UPI ID/QR — displayed to parents on their receipt |

---

### 6. 📄 Notes
**Purpose:** Upload and share study material with students/batches.

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Upload Notes | PDF, Images, Word docs; linked to a specific batch or 'All Batches' |
| Notes List | Title, Subject, Date uploaded, Batch, Download button |
| Student-Facing View | (via login or public link) — students access their batch notes |
| Organize by Subject/Topic | Folders or tags per subject area |
| Delete / Replace | Manage uploaded documents |

---

### 7. 📝 Tests
**Purpose:** Create, assign, and track test results. Two modes:

#### Mode A — Online Test (Question Creator)
| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Create Test | Title, Subject, Batch, Date, Duration, Total Marks |
| Add Questions | MCQ, Short Answer, True/False question types |
| Assign to Batch | Students receive notification; can take test via their student link |
| Auto-Grading | MCQ auto-scored; short answers need manual review |
| Results Dashboard | Average score, top performers, below-threshold alerts |

#### Mode B — Offline Test (PDF + Manual Scoring)
| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Upload Test Paper | PDF upload (optional) |
| Enter Scores | Table: student name + score input per student |
| Score Summary | Average, highest, lowest, rank list |
| Export Results | PDF marksheet / CSV |

---

### 8. 📊 Reports
**Purpose:** Aggregated analytics for the teacher.

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Attendance Report | Per batch or per student — monthly trend |
| Fee Collection Report | Total collected vs. total pending this month |
| Test Performance Report | Average scores per batch, subject trends |
| Student Progress Report | Combined: Attendance % + Fee status + Test avg for each student |
| Export | PDF/CSV download for all report types |
| Date Range Filter | Custom date range selector |

---

### 9. 📢 Announcements
**Purpose:** Broadcast messages to students/parents.

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Create Announcement | Title, Message, Target (All / Specific Batch) |
| Channels | In-app feed + WhatsApp (via wa.me link generation) + SMS (optional) |
| Schedule | Post now or schedule for later |
| Announcement History | List of past broadcasts + delivery status |
| Pin Announcement | Pin important notices to top of student feed |

---

### 10. 🌐 Public Profile (Teacher Page)
**Purpose:** SEO-indexed page for student discovery.

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Teacher Hero | Photo, Name, Subjects, Tagline, Location |
| About Me | Rich text bio + years of experience |
| Qualifications | Inline list (B.Ed, M.Sc, etc.) |
| Gallery | Photos of classroom, results screenshots |
| Open Batches | Cards for batches with vacancies — "X seats left" |
| Testimonials | Teacher adds student/parent reviews |
| Enquiry Form | Lead capture: Name, Phone, Grade, Message → notifies teacher dashboard |
| Sticky CTA | "Enquire Now" always visible on mobile scroll |
| Share Profile | Shareable URL + QR Code generator |
| Verified Badge | Shown after admin approval |

---

### 11. 🔍 Search & Discovery
**Purpose:** Landing page for prospective students to find teachers.

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Search Bar | By subject, location, grade |
| Filters | Subject, Location, Fee Range, Rating, Availability |
| Teacher Cards | Photo, Name, Subjects, Rating, Location, "View Profile" CTA |
| Featured / Promoted | Optional paid slot for teachers to appear at top |
| SEO-Optimized URLs | `/teachers/math/mumbai` style landing pages |

---

### 12. ⚙️ Settings (Teacher Account)
> **New module — not in original folders but essential.**

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Profile Settings | Edit name, photo, bio, subjects, location |
| Notification Preferences | Toggle SMS / WhatsApp alerts |
| Subscription Plan | View current plan (Free/Pro), upgrade CTA |
| Connected Apps | (Future: WhatsApp Business, Google Calendar) |
| Danger Zone | Delete account, export all data |

---

### 13. 🛡️ Admin Panel (Internal)
**Purpose:** Alogyan staff CRM.

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Teacher Verification Queue | Approve/reject with ID proof side-by-side view |
| User Management | Search by phone/ID, view full account, suspend/reactivate |
| Subscription Management | View MRR, active plans, manual plan adjustments |
| Support Tickets | Internal notes on teacher accounts |
| Platform Announcements | Broadcast to all teachers |
| Analytics | New signups/day, active teachers, churn |

---

## 💡 Suggested Additions (Beyond Original Plan)

| # | Idea | Why |
|---|------|-----|
| 1 | **Student/Parent Login Portal** | Students access their own notes, test results, fee receipts |
| 2 | **Settings Module** | Essential for profile edits + plan management — currently missing from folder structure |
| 3 | **WhatsApp Integration (wa.me links)** | Already in UX flows — formalise as a first-class feature, not just a button |
| 4 | **Notifications Center** | In-app feed for leads, payment alerts, system messages |
| 5 | **Leads / Enquiries Module** | Dedicated space to manage enquiries from public profile (Accept → Convert to Student) |

